title: Le Jardin Nomade
description: Le Jardin Nomade is a small community garden open to all residents for a collective participation in culture of individual or shared plots. It is managed by the St. Bernard District Association. Many events invite all residents to gather around convivial moments: a neighborhood soup takes place one Saturday a month throughout the year. Each brings his vegetables or ideas of soup.
